# File Structure for Vercel Deployment

Create these files in your GitHub repository in this exact structure:

```
roebling-view-dashboard/
├── package.json
├── .gitignore
├── public/
│   └── index.html
└── src/
    ├── App.jsx
    ├── index.js
    └── index.css
```

---

